41BC</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName>
<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="bgu;10;1994" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">BGU10,1994</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Δημήτριος Ζήνωνι χ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αίρ</unclear>ειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>γράφεις μοι δοῦναι Ἀντι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">πά</unclear>τρωι 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐκ τῶν περιόντων οἰναρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ίω</unclear>ν <expan><ex cert="high"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δραχμὰς</unclear></ex></expan> <num value="100">ρ</num>· 

    <lb n="4"/>ἔστιν δὲ τὰ περιόντα <expan>κερ<ex cert="high">άμια</ex></expan> <num value="8">η</num>, ἐν οἷς 

    <lb n="5"/>ἔνεστιν <num value="3">γ</num> τὰ διαφωνοῦντα, 

    <lb n="6"/>ἃ καὶ ἔγευσαν Ἀντίπατρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>ν καὶ 

    <lb n="7"/>Νίκανδρον, ὥστε μηδὲ δραχμῆς 

    <lb n="8"/>τὸν χόα ἄξιον εἶναι. καὶ εἰ μὴ τὴν 

    <lb n="9"/>ἐπιγραφὴν ἑώρων, τοὺς παρα-

    <lb n="10"/>κομίζοντας ἂν ᾐτιώμην. καλῶς 

    <lb n="11"/>οὖν ποιήσεις εὐώδους ἀποστεί-

    <lb n="12"/>λας κεράμια πλέονα. ἱκανὸς γάρ 

    <lb n="13"/><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">και</del> <add place="supralinear">τις</add> ὄχλος ἐνδημεῖ διὰ τὸ καὶ τὰς 

    <lb n="14"/>ὠνὰς πωλεῖσθαι καὶ ζητοῦσι 

    <lb n="15"/>εὐώδη καὶ ἅμα τὸν περιόντα 

    <lb n="16"/>ἐξώσει. ἀπέστειλα δέ σοι καὶ 

    <lb n="17"/>πρότερον τὸν παρ᾽ αὐτοῦ λόγον 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="18"/>καὶ νῦν ἐπὶ κεφαλαίου ὧν 

    <lb n="19"/>τὸ καθ᾽ ἓν <num value="1"/> ὑπάρχει ἵνα εἰδῇς 

    <lb n="20"/>ἕως Μεχεὶρ <num value="11">ια</num> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμαὶ</ex></expan> <num value="190">ρϙ</num> κα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὶ</supplied> 

    <lb n="21"/>μετὰ λόγον <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">ἐπισκεψάμενος</del> 

    <lb n="22"/>γραφήσεταί σοι. 

    <lb n="23"/>ἔρρωσο <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="6"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ϛ</unclear></num> Μεχεὶρ <num value="15">ι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear></num>. 

    <lb n="24"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Ζ</unclear>ήνωνι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.1861" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1861" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-242" notBefore="-242" type="textDate" value="-0242-04-05">5. Apr. 242 v.Chr. (Jahr unsicher)</date></p><p><date notAfter="-241" notBefore="-241" type="textDate" value="-0241-04-04">4. Apr. 241 v.Chr. (Jahr unsicher)</date></p></div><div n="meta.1861" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Datierung nach dem Finanzjahr. Alternativdatierung: 4. Apr. 241 v.Chr. Zur Datierung vgl. BL VIII, S. 204.</p></div><div n="meta.1861" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Zen. Pestm.</title><biblScope type="numbers">30</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1861</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0229</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">30</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0229;;30" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1861" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">204</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.1861" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">BGU X, Tafel XXII</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.1861" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Pu